                <div style="background:#222;padding:10px;border-radius:5px;margin-bottom:15px;border:1px solid #444;">
                    <div class="ling-row" style="margin-bottom:5px;">
                        <label style="color:#F3BA2F;font-weight:bold;">ğŸš¨ å“¨å…µæ¨¡å¼</label>
